  <li>re-written the validator for add-ons into JavaScript and its now mirroring the rules from Firefox</li>
  <li>re-written the discovery pane in Firefox and the <a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/">AMO mobile pages</a></li>
  <li>written 11 blog posts (&lt;a href=‚Äù<a href="https://blog.mozilla.org/addons/2015/12/21/webextensions-in-firefox-45-2/">Firefox 45</a> to <a href="https://blog.mozilla.org/addons/2017/08/10/webextensions-firefox-56/">Firefox 56</a>) on WebExtensions status</li>
