<p>‚Ä¶ there‚Äôs a ton of things I‚Äôve missed, apologies to everyone. And <b>we aren‚Äôt done</b>, we‚Äôve got 6 weeks till the cut off for 57 and then another month or two as it rolls out to release.</p>

<p>What‚Äôs more important is the <a href="http://mckay.pub/2016-04-17-addons-old/">possibilities for the future</a>, this:</p>

<ul>
  <li>releases the shackles around Firefox developers that extensions caused</li>
  <li>improves the security and performance for our users</li>
